{"tid":555897,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[WOW] 無國界記者組織 呼籲記者停用中國 iCloud","createTime":"2018-02-10T03:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T09:41:49.000Z","uid":28563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8b0e2a84bfe387a618d2486be2f9757e0230e9","tid":555897,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T03:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/07/%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%8C%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-icloud/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594-%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-icloud%2F&d=9kWRrrbm%2Fk7%2Bxn%2BO0qEwoAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=350d5ef8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/07/%E7%84%A1%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%8C%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-icloud/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前，無國界記者組織發表聲明，敦促記者在 2 月底前停止使用中國的 iPhone的 iCloud 雲端服務，並更改用戶國家設定。組織表示，這是為了保護記者的安全。早前駐華外國記者協會發表報告指，中國的採訪環境惡化，甚至有外國記者發現通訊被監聽，相關新聞機構亦遭當局恐嚇，情況令人關注。<br />\n<br />\n為了符合中國法規，由 2 月 28 日起，Apple 在中國的 iCloud 服務，將轉由具中國政府背景的「雲上貴州」公司營運，國家或區域設定為中國的 Apple 帳戶將受到影響。無國界記者組織（Reporters Without Borders）台北辦事處主任 Cedric Alviani 表示，無國界記者組織的成立，是要保護記者和保護言論自由，並指責 Apple 既然選擇符合中國政府要求，iCloud 就不再是能保障存放資料安全的地方，派駐中國的記者如果繼續使用此服務，會遇到很大的風險。<br />\n中國 iCloud 使用者條款特別列明：蘋果公司和雲上貴州有權訪問您在此服務中存儲的所有資料<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Apple 在今年1月時曾經表示擁有強大的資料隱私和安全保護機制，並且不會在我們任何系統創建後門。但根據「iCloud（由雲上貴州運營）條款與條件」，使用者條款特別列明：「您理解並同意，蘋果公司和雲上貴州有權訪問您在此服務中存儲的所有資料，包括根據適用法律向對方和在彼此之間共用、交換和披露所有用戶資料（包括內容）的權利。」<br />\n<br />\nCedric Alviani 表示，Apple 富可敵國，現金流和芬蘭國內生產總值相約，其實有能力和中國政府交涉，而 Apple 這次的讓步，只會開始一個壞的先例，令 Google 和 Facebook 也一直努力想打入中國市場的公司，可能也要向中國政府作出讓步。"},{"pid":"e2a7e9a9b7cbecaa5e9722dd73bc87939744407f","tid":555897,"uid":9621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:25:01.000Z","msg":"我個apple id係香港，但係佢個網都係寫我用緊大陸iCloud? 可以點改？"},{"pid":"fd045c73e1a9f05800707b3940e42535a41adb35","tid":555897,"uid":9621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.icloud.com/optout/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icloud.com%2Foptout%2F&d=9kWRrrbm%2Fk7%2Bxn%2BO0qEwoAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=a28e96c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.icloud.com/optout/</a>"},{"pid":"1a6259d5724755ec9f05a3b09b783fc6ea9d9cc8","tid":555897,"uid":97059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"Apple 又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619e0c1a592639da45d9018e5b8dea2ecf9d625e","tid":555897,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc54f7465fbea9e7f0451f4816dab40913bc8a6","tid":555897,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T16:49:02.000Z","msg":"冇人理"},{"pid":"161a0f4fb4d39bac4a5530a92ef87dbbbdbdfa22","tid":555897,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">蘋果公司和雲上貴州有權訪問您在此服務中存儲的所有資料</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪寫清楚會攞你資料，大家就覺得無野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee13817b163ed5a2b8033a44e5941f5fd51de2f3","tid":555897,"uid":1557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"161a0f4fb4d39bac4a5530a92ef87dbbbdbdfa22","tid":555897,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">蘋果公司和雲上貴州有權訪問您在此服務中存儲的所有資料</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces